Package org.lappsgrid.client

Clients that can be used to access web services running on the Lappsgrid.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractClient
    The AbstractClient provides all of the functionality needed to interact with a LAPPS web service.
    AbstractSoapClient
    This class is not used and will be deprecated in an upcoming release.
    DataSourceClient
    The DataSourceClient provides several helper methods that parse the JSON returned by the service into normal Java types.
    Server
    A class to hold information about a particular server on the LAPPS grid.
    ServiceClient
    The ServiceClient does not add any functionality, it is simply provides a way to instantiate the AbstractClient.
